<title>qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk)3 .. wʿynyã ʿlyk
 (ạ̉nạ mstnyk)3 .. tmd ly ạ̹ydyk
 1- qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk .. ạ̹nt kl mạlyã
 qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk .. wbḥbk yạ fạdyã
 mljạ̉y wḥṣny .. ṣkẖrty ạlqwyẗ
 (wfrḥy dwmaⁿạ fyk)2
 2- qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk .. lạ̉nk ḥbytny
 qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk .. lmạ f ḍʿfy sẖfytny
 ạ̹ydk ạlḥlwẗ sẖạltny .. wf ḥḍnk ḍmtny
 (kạ̹bn mdll lyk)2
 3- qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk .. yswʿ lạ swạk
 qlby ạ̹tʿlq byk .. rby mạ ạ̉sẖhạk
 mlkt kyạny .. wqlby wyạ lsạny
 (dwmaⁿạ yhtfwạ byk)2</lyrics>
